1. *Kovač* je majstor koji pravi i popravlja metalne predmete. (Smith is a craftsman who makes and repairs metal objects.)
2. U selu ima *kovačnice* gde meštani nose svoje alatke na popravku. (There are smithies in the village where locals take their tools for repair.)
3. Moj otac je radio kao *kovački* pomoćnik pre nego što se preselio u grad. (My father worked as a smith's assistant before he moved to the city.)
4. *Kovačnica* je zauzela veliki deo radionice zbog velikih mašina koje se koriste za kovanje metala. (The smithy took up a large part of the workshop due to the large machines used for forging metal.)
5. *Kovačević* je čest prezime u Srbiji. (Kovačević is a common surname in Serbia.)